ise and robust measurement of rotation periods, and more accurate\nstellar parameter measurements will enable continued improvements in the age\nestimates of these important exoplanet host stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Jan 2023 06:38:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-08"}
