rium many-body physics and overcomes both\nthe conceptual constraints of dynamical density functional theory as well as\nthe limited availability of its analytical functional approximations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Jan 2023 10:46:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Mar 2023 21:03:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-11"}
