onal support for the conjecture. We also, via new results on\nthe invariance of the essential spectral radius under locally-conformal\n$C^{1,\\beta}$ diffeomorphisms, show that the spectral radius conjecture holds\nfor all Lipschitz curvilinear polyhedra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Jan 2023 14:18:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2023 11:29:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-06"}
